How are skills supposed to work?

Skills
1. Skills are supposed to be added by Mods and Users
2. Skills are synchronized from Server to Client
3. Skills have Parent Skills
4. Multiple types of Skill Points can be required to unlock a Skill

Skill Trees
1. Each skill can be within multiple skill trees
2. Skill Trees should be specified within JSON Files
3. Skill Trees are "Skills" by them self and can be linked within other Skill Tree's

Skill Points
1. Skill Points should have an icon
2. Skill Points should have categories
3. Skill Points are levelable, reaching a level gives you a Skill Point (optional per skill point)